  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">The time period spanning from year 2000 to 2021 during which maternal mortality observations were recorded for the Arab World.&lt;SEP&gt;2000年至2021年的时间段，巴林的孕产妇死亡率数据在此期间被观察和记录。&lt;SEP&gt;The time period spanning from year 2000 to year 2021 during which maternal mortality data was recorded in the Euro area.&lt;SEP&gt;The time period covering Iceland's maternal mortality observations from year 2000 through year 2021.&lt;SEP&gt;The time period spanning from year 2000 to 2021 during which Japan recorded maternal mortality data.&lt;SEP&gt;2000-2021 represents the time period during which maternal mortality data for Korea, Rep. was observed and recorded.</data>
